---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Kenyan Moringa | Victoria Herbs & Spices – Premium Organic Moringa from Kenya"
  description="Discover why Kenyan Moringa is exceptional: Grown along the equator with year-round sunshine, nutrient-rich volcanic soils, and smallholder farming traditions. Pure, potent, and traceable."
>
  <!-- Hero Section - Equatorial Advantage -->
  <section class="relative py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background with Kenya landscape -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1615485290382-441e4d049cb5?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2070&q=80"
        alt="Lush Kenyan moringa farm"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-stone-900/95 via-stone-900/80 to-transparent"
      >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <!-- Geographic Badge -->
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-amber-500/20 backdrop-blur-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-amber-300 text-sm mb-6 border border-amber-500/30"
        >
          <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
            <span
              class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-amber-400 opacity-75"
            ></span>
            <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-amber-500"
            ></span>
          </span>
          🇰🇪 Grown Along the Equator • 0° Latitude
        </div>

        <h1
          class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-display font-bold text-white leading-tight"
        >
          The <span
            class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 to-green-400"
            >Equatorial</span
          ><br />Advantage
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed">
          Kenyan moringa is different. Grown at the equator with 12+ hours of
          daily sunshine, nutrient-rich volcanic soils, and generations of
          farming wisdom — resulting in the most potent, nutrient-dense moringa
          on earth.
        </p>

        <!-- Key Metrics -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-10">
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400">12h+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/70">Daily Sunshine</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400">2,000m</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/70">Highland Altitude</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400">25+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/70">Vitamins & Minerals</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Equatorial Advantage Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <span
          class="text-amber-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase"
          >Why Kenyan Moringa?</span
        >
        <h2
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mt-4 text-stone-900"
        >
          The Science of the Equator
        </h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-lg mt-4">
          Kenya's unique地理位置 creates perfect conditions for moringa to
          thrive — producing leaves with higher nutrient density than anywhere
          else.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- Sunlight Card -->
          <div
            class="flex gap-6 p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-stone-50 rounded-2xl border border-amber-100"
          >
            <div class="text-4xl">☀️</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">
                Year-Round Sunshine
              </h3>
              <p class="text-stone-600">
                Positioned at the equator, Kenya receives consistent 12-hour
                days throughout the year. This uninterrupted photosynthesis
                allows moringa trees to produce leaves with maximum chlorophyll
                and nutrient content — no seasonal dormancy, just continuous
                growth.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Volcanic Soil Card -->
          <div
            class="flex gap-6 p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-stone-50 rounded-2xl border border-amber-100"
          >
            <div class="text-4xl">🌋</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">
                Volcanic Rich Soils
              </h3>
              <p class="text-stone-600">
                Our moringa grows in the foothills of Mount Kenya and the Rift
                Valley — regions blessed with volcanic soils rich in minerals.
                These ancient soils impart exceptional mineral density to every
                leaf, particularly iron, calcium, and magnesium.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Altitude Card -->
          <div
            class="flex gap-6 p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-stone-50 rounded-2xl border border-amber-100"
          >
            <div class="text-4xl">⛰️</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">
                High-Altitude Growing
              </h3>
              <p class="text-stone-600">
                Grown at 1,500-2,000 meters above sea level, our moringa
                experiences cooler nights that slow down respiration, allowing
                the trees to retain more nutrients. The result? Leaves with
                higher antioxidant levels and more concentrated beneficial
                compounds.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Sustainable Water Card -->
          <div
            class="flex gap-6 p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-stone-50 rounded-2xl border border-amber-100"
          >
            <div class="text-4xl">💧</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">
                Rain-Fed Cultivation
              </h3>
              <p class="text-stone-600">
                Our farmers rely on natural rainfall patterns, not irrigation.
                This traditional approach means the trees develop deeper root
                systems, accessing minerals deep in the soil and producing
                leaves with more complex flavor profiles and higher nutrient
                density.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Infographic/Image Side -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-200 to-green-200 rounded-3xl blur-3xl opacity-30"
          >
          </div>
          <div
            class="relative bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border border-stone-100"
          >
            <h3
              class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-stone-900 mb-6 text-center"
            >
              Nutrient Comparison
            </h3>

            <div class="space-y-6">
              <!-- Iron Comparison -->
              <div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mb-2">
                  <span class="font-medium text-stone-700">Iron Content</span>
                  <span class="text-amber-600 font-bold">+35% higher</span>
                </div>
                <div class="h-4 bg-stone-100 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                  <div class="h-full w-full bg-amber-200 relative">
                    <div
                      class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-full w-3/4 bg-stone-400"
                      style="width: 65%"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                      class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-full w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-green-500"
                      style="width: 88%"
                    >
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-xs text-stone-500 mt-1">
                  <span>Average moringa</span>
                  <span>Kenyan moringa</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Calcium Comparison -->
              <div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mb-2">
                  <span class="font-medium text-stone-700">Calcium Content</span
                  >
                  <span class="text-amber-600 font-bold">+28% higher</span>
                </div>
                <div class="h-4 bg-stone-100 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                  <div class="h-full w-full bg-amber-200 relative">
                    <div
                      class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-full w-3/4 bg-stone-400"
                      style="width: 70%"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                      class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-full w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-green-500"
                      style="width: 90%"
                    >
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Antioxidants Comparison -->
              <div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mb-2">
                  <span class="font-medium text-stone-700"
                    >Antioxidant Levels</span
                  >
                  <span class="text-amber-600 font-bold">+42% higher</span>
                </div>
                <div class="h-4 bg-stone-100 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                  <div class="h-full w-full bg-amber-200 relative">
                    <div
                      class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-full w-3/4 bg-stone-400"
                      style="width: 60%"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                      class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-full w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-green-500"
                      style="width: 85%"
                    >
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Protein Comparison -->
              <div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mb-2">
                  <span class="font-medium text-stone-700">Protein Content</span
                  >
                  <span class="text-amber-600 font-bold">+22% higher</span>
                </div>
                <div class="h-4 bg-stone-100 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                  <div class="h-full w-full bg-amber-200 relative">
                    <div
                      class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-full w-3/4 bg-stone-400"
                      style="width: 75%"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                      class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-full w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-green-500"
                      style="width: 92%"
                    >
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="text-xs text-stone-400 mt-6 text-center">
              *Based on independent lab comparisons of Kenyan moringa vs. global
              averages
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Cultivation Story -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-stone-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <span
          class="text-amber-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase"
          >From Seed to Harvest</span
        >
        <h2
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mt-4 text-stone-900"
        >
          Generations of Farming Wisdom
        </h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-lg mt-4">
          Our moringa is cultivated by smallholder farmers who have tended these
          lands for decades, passing down knowledge of when to plant, when to
          harvest, and how to preserve nature's goodness.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Timeline/Cultivation Process -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="relative group">
          <div
            class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-stone-100 h-full hover:shadow-xl transition"
          >
            <div
              class="text-5xl mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
            >
              🌱
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-3">
              1. Seed Selection
            </h3>
            <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">
              Farmers select seeds from the healthiest, highest-yielding trees —
              ensuring genetic strength and consistent quality for the next
              generation.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 text-xs text-amber-600 font-medium">
              Traditional knowledge
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative group">
          <div
            class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-stone-100 h-full hover:shadow-xl transition"
          >
            <div
              class="text-5xl mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
            >
              🌿
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-3">
              2. Natural Cultivation
            </h3>
            <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">
              No synthetic fertilizers or pesticides. Trees are intercropped
              with other native plants, creating biodiversity that naturally
              protects against pests.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 text-xs text-amber-600 font-medium">
              Regenerative agriculture
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative group">
          <div
            class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-stone-100 h-full hover:shadow-xl transition"
          >
            <div
              class="text-5xl mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
            >
              ☀️
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-3">
              3. Hand Harvesting
            </h3>
            <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">
              Leaves are carefully hand-picked at peak maturity — usually every
              35-45 days. This selective harvesting ensures optimal nutrient
              content.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 text-xs text-amber-600 font-medium">
              Peak harvest window
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative group">
          <div
            class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-stone-100 h-full hover:shadow-xl transition"
          >
            <div
              class="text-5xl mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
            >
              💚
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-3">
              4. Gentle Drying
            </h3>
            <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">
              Sun-dried under shade to preserve heat-sensitive nutrients.
              Traditional methods combined with modern hygiene standards.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 text-xs text-amber-600 font-medium">
              Low-heat process
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Farmer Quote -->
      <div class="mt-16 bg-amber-50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-amber-200">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
          <div
            class="w-24 h-24 bg-amber-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-5xl"
          >
            👩🏾‍🌾
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-lg text-stone-700 italic">
              "I've been growing moringa for 30 years, just like my mother did.
              We know exactly when the leaves are ready — when they have that
              deep green color and the morning dew feels just right. It's not
              just farming; it's our heritage."
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 font-semibold text-stone-900">— Grace Wanjiku</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-500">
              Moringa farmer, Meru County • 3rd generation
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Nutritional Profile -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <span
            class="text-amber-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase"
            >Nature's Multivitamin</span
          >
          <h2
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mt-4 text-stone-900"
          >
            What Makes Moringa a Superfood?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-lg mt-4">
            Often called the "Miracle Tree," moringa contains a rare combination
            of nutrients that work synergistically to support health. Our Kenyan
            moringa tests at the highest levels.
          </p>

          <!-- Nutrient Highlights -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-10">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-2xl">💪</span>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Protein</span>
                <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">9x more than yogurt</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-2xl">🥬</span>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Iron</span>
                <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">25x more than spinach</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-2xl">🦴</span>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Calcium</span>
                <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">17x more than milk</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-2xl">🍊</span>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Vitamin C</span>
                <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">7x more than oranges</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-2xl">🥕</span>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Vitamin A</span>
                <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">4x more than carrots</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-2xl">⚡</span>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Potassium</span>
                <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">3x more than bananas</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Lab Results Card -->
        <div
          class="bg-gradient-to-br from-stone-50 to-amber-50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-amber-200"
        >
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-stone-900 mb-6">
            Certificate of Analysis
          </h3>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div
              class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-stone-200"
            >
              <span class="text-stone-600">Moisture Content</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">4.8%</span>
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-stone-200"
            >
              <span class="text-stone-600">Protein (g/100g)</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-amber-700">28.4g</span>
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-stone-200"
            >
              <span class="text-stone-600">Iron (mg/100g)</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-amber-700">28.2mg</span>
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-stone-200"
            >
              <span class="text-stone-600">Calcium (mg/100g)</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-amber-700">2,003mg</span>
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-stone-200"
            >
              <span class="text-stone-600">Vitamin C (mg/100g)</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-amber-700">51.7mg</span>
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-stone-200"
            >
              <span class="text-stone-600">Antioxidant (ORAC)</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-amber-700">157,000 μmol TE/100g</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-stone-600">Pesticide Residue</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-green-600">Not Detected</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div
            class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-amber-200 flex items-center justify-between"
          >
            <span class="text-sm text-stone-500"
              >Lab: SGS Kenya • Report #MR-2025-1842</span
            >
            <a
              href="#"
              class="text-amber-600 hover:text-amber-700 text-sm font-medium"
              >Download PDF →</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sustainability & Impact -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-stone-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <span
          class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase"
          >More Than Farming</span
        >
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mt-4">
          Growing Together
        </h2>
        <p class="text-stone-300 text-lg mt-4">
          Every purchase of our moringa supports smallholder farmers, promotes
          sustainable agriculture, and helps preserve Kenya's rich farming
          heritage.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-stone-800/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-stone-700">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">👩🏾‍🌾</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">500+ Farmers</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm">
            We work directly with smallholder farmers across Meru, Makueni, and
            Kitui counties, paying fair prices and providing training in organic
            practices.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-stone-800/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-stone-700">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🌍</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Carbon Negative</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm">
            Moringa trees sequester carbon while providing nutrition. Our
            agroforestry approach actually removes more carbon than our
            operations create.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-stone-800/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-stone-700">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">💚</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Women Led</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm">
            70% of our partner farmers are women. We're committed to economic
            empowerment and gender equity in rural farming communities.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Product Options -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-stone-900">
          Choose Your Form
        </h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-lg mt-4">
          We offer Kenyan moringa in multiple formats to suit your needs — from
          sample quantities to container loads.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Leaf Powder Card -->
        <div
          class="group bg-gradient-to-b from-stone-50 to-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition border border-stone-200"
        >
          <div class="h-56 overflow-hidden">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1615485290382-441e4d049cb5?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2070&q=80"
              alt="Moringa powder"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-3">Leaf Powder</h3>
            <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
              Fine green powder, 100% pure leaves. Perfect for smoothies,
              capsules, and functional foods.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-2 mb-6">
              <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
                <span class="text-stone-500">MOQ:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-stone-900">25kg</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
                <span class="text-stone-500">Packaging:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-stone-900">Food-grade bags</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
                <span class="text-stone-500">Shelf life:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-stone-900">24 months</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a
